Following fixes has been made:

1. Additionsl components appeared since v7.0 now being installed (sfreflect and sflaunch);
2. System-wide CFLAGS received appropriate respect;
3. System md5 library used instead of port's own;
4. GSM library now used properly from GSM port instead of SF port;
5. Portlint is happy now;
6. WWWs removed from Makefile and added to pkg/DESCR.
